TITLE: Enabling/Disabling Task Pane Auto-Open via Office JS API
DESCRIPTION: Provides two JavaScript functions using the Office JavaScript API. 'setAutoOpenOn' uses 'Office.context.document.settings.set' to add a document setting named 'Office.AutoShowTaskpaneWithDocument' with a value of 'true', enabling auto-open. 'setAutoOpenOff' uses 'settings.remove' to delete this setting, disabling auto-open. Both functions save the changes asynchronously and display a notification.
