LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
protected override async Task OnAfterRenderAsync(bool firstRender)
{
  if (firstRender)
  {
    JSModule = await JSRuntime.InvokeAsync<IJSObjectReference>("import", "./Pages/Index.razor.js");
  }
}
```

